name: Franklyn Moss
description: I see myself as caring and compassionate, and value special friendships. I enjoy getting out and about but am just as happy pottering in my garden, cooking in my kitchen, and sitting in front of the fire with a lovely glass of wine. Would love to do more traveling, especially to the places I have not yet explored. Life would not be complete without good humour, great conversation, yummy food, (including chocolate), and someone special to share this with.
